      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: gridPositions.Array.data[48].z
      value: 12
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: interactableObjects.Array.size
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[0]'
      value: "Hey there! I\u2019m Vulpes."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[1]'
      value: "I absolutely love machines\u2026 but cooking? Ugh, not my thing at
        all. "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[2]'
      value: "Still\u2026 I\u2019ve always dreamed of running my own little restaurant. 
        So, I guess I\u2019ll need your help to make it work!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[3]'
      value: "I\u2019m obsessed with Vietnamese banh mi\u2026and I\u2019ve got a
        few very handy machines right here!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[4]'
      value: "So\u2026 how about it? Will you help me build a fully automated Banh
        Mi restaurant - with NO STAFF needed?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[5]'
      value: We can do it, let me tell you!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[6]'
      value: A Grabber can pick up ANY item and move it to another place
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[7]'
      value: Try using a Grabber to take flour from the container and move it to
        the Robomixer!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[8]'
      value: Buy Grabber in the shop. Be careful, your budget is limited
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[9]'
      value: blank
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[10]'
      value: Drag & drop to place the Grabber and rotate it to the correct direction
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[11]'
      value: Press RUN button to run your setup
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[12]'
      value: blank
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[13]'
      value: You can upgrade a Grabber into a Smart Grabber. A Smart Grabber lets
        you choose which item it will pick up.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[14]'
      value: "Trust me, you\u2019ll need a smarter machine to avoid picking up unprocessed
        dough by mistake"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[15]'
      value: Try to move the shaped dough into the oven to get your first banh mi.
        Good luck!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[16]'
      value: "All the recipes you need are in the Recipe. Check it now to make today\u2019s
        dish!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7594121445791573636, guid: 9cae142b8cb5c6545851fdaeb822d92c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'tutorialTextList.Array.data[17]'
      value: blank
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
